---
title: Louisiana BBQ Beef Rissoles with Kumara Fries & Mixed Salad
description: These rissoles are bursting with the tried and true flavour of our Southern Louisiana spice blend and tangy BBQ sauce. On the
side, we've got a bright salad, studded with charred corn and wholesome oven-baked kumara fries for a splendid finish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-bbq-beef-rissoles-4507f71c.jpg
